## Productize CLI {{ .Version }}

Welcome to the latest release of the Productize CLI!

### Installation

#### Homebrew
```bash
brew install --cask itseffi/productize/productize
```

#### NPM
```bash
npm install -g @productize/cli
```

#### Binary Download
Download the appropriate `productize_{{ .Version }}_<os>_<arch>.tar.gz` asset for your platform and extract it.

#### Go Install
```bash
go install github.com/itseffi/productize/cmd/productize@{{ .Tag }}
```
